  <main class="my-5 ">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to A One Global, one of the best overseas education consultants in India. By using our services, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions. Please
        review them carefully. If you do not agree to these terms and conditions, you should not use our services.
      </p>

