      <p>A One Global provides consultancy services for overseas education, including but not limited to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">
          <strong>University Admission</strong>
          <ul>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Assistance with university admission processes for higher education abroad.</li>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Guidance on application procedures, documentation, and deadlines.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">
          <strong>Work Permit Process</strong>
          <ul>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Support in obtaining work permits for career opportunities abroad.</li>
