            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Assistance in obtaining health and medical insurance for studying abroad.</li>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Guidance on selecting appropriate insurance plans and completing applications.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">
          <strong>Overseas Internship</strong>
          <ul>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Support in securing internships abroad for early-career professionals.</li>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Guidance on application procedures and internship opportunities.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">
          <strong>Education Loan</strong>
          <ul>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Assistance in managing and obtaining education loans for studying abroad.</li>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Guidance on loan options, application processes, and required documentation.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">
          <strong>Coaching Assistance</strong>
          <ul>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Support in preparing for various educational requirements and exams.</li>
            <li style="list-style: disclosure-closed;">Provision of resources and guidance to help achieve educational goals.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Eligibility</h2>
      <p>
        To use our services, you must be of legal age and have the authority to enter into a binding contract. By using our services, you represent and warrant that you meet these eligibility
        requirements.
      </p>

      <h2>University Admission</h2>
      <p>
        Our university admission services are designed to assist professionals seeking higher education opportunities. We provide information and guidance on university programs and the application
        process. However, the final decision regarding admission rests with the respective universities.
      </p>

      <h2>Work Permit Process</h2>
      <p>
        Our work permit process services are aimed at professionals seeking career advancement opportunities abroad. We provide guidance on the application process for work permits, but the final
        approval is at the discretion of the relevant authorities.
      </p>

      <h2>Health Insurance</h2>
      <p>
        We offer guidance on obtaining health and medical insurance for individuals pursuing higher education abroad. Our role is to provide information and assist with the application process. The
        final decision on insurance approval lies with the insurance providers.
      </p>

      <h2>Overseas Internship</h2>
      <p>
        We assist early-career professionals in securing internships abroad. Our services include providing information on available internship opportunities and the application process. The final
        selection and approval for internships are determined by the host organizations.
      </p>

      <h2>Education Loan</h2>
      <p>
        We provide assistance in managing education loans for higher education abroad. Our services include providing information on available loan options and guidance on the application process. The
        final approval of loans is subject to the discretion of the lending institutions.
      </p>

      <h2>Coaching Assistance</h2>
      <p>
        Our coaching assistance services are designed to help students prepare for various educational requirements. We provide guidance and resources to support students' educational and career
        goals.
